<plot>"Global Exaggeration," chronicles three freedom fighters in a battle against a global enemy, the environment. Michaels, a seasoned soldier, leads a three man squad, which includes former special forces soldier, Stokes, as well as Gregs, the youngest and least experienced soldier of the group. The three men are fighting against the biggest threat to the safety of all men on Earth, global warming. Equipped with guns, knives, CFC canisters, and sun block, these soldiers are fighting for the lives of all the people in the world.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?217195</url></doc>
